(************************************************************
 *                      IMITATOR MODEL                      
 *
 * Toy example to test the subtleties of AF with actions synthesis
 *
 * Description     : Toy example to test the subtleties of AF with actions synthesis. Correctness should be achieved if "p3 = 1 and p1 <= 5 and a and (not b OR p2 > 5)".
 * Correctness     : AF(lG1)
 * Source          : Étienne André
 * Author          : Étienne André
 * Modeling        : Étienne André
 * Input by        : Étienne André
